OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1781179881
OL,3,CWales secure top spot in World Cup
OL,4,Cqualifying after win over Czech
OL,5,CRepublic
OL,7,FWales Women have finished top of their
OL,8,FWorld Cup qualifying group after a 3-1
OL,9,Fvictory over Czech Republic on Tuesday
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,12,FBoth teams were already destined for
OL,13,Fthe play-offs, all that was left to
OL,14,Fdecide at the Cardiff City Stadium was
OL,15,Fthe path they would have to take.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1781179881
OL,3,CWales secure top spot in World Cup
OL,4,Cqualifying after win over Czech
OL,5,CRepublic
OL,7,FWales' start was disastrous. A long
OL,8,Fball over the top from Czech
OL,9,Fgoalkeeper Olivie Lukasova was
OL,10,Fmisjudged by Rhiannon Roberts. It put
OL,11,FMichaela Khyrova one-on-one with Safia
OL,12,FMiddleton-Patel and she slotted it
OL,13,Finto the corner, giving the visitors
OL,14,Fthe ascendency.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1781179881
OL,3,CWales secure top spot in World Cup
OL,4,Cqualifying after win over Czech
OL,5,CRepublic
OL,7,FBut Rhian Wilkinson's side were level
OL,8,Fbefore 10 minutes had elapsed. The
OL,9,Fball bobbled into the path of Sophie
OL,10,FIngle just inside the visitors' area
OL,11,Ffrom a throw-in. She teed up Lily
OL,12,FWoodham, who drove the ball into the
OL,13,Fbottom left-hand corner to equalise on
OL,14,Fher 50th cap.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1781179881
OL,3,CWales secure top spot in World Cup
OL,4,Cqualifying after win over Czech
OL,5,CRepublic
OL,7,FWales pressed and harried with energy
OL,8,Ffor the first half hour and there was
OL,9,Fan edge to proceedings. Hannah Cain
OL,10,Fdrew the ire of the Czech defence when
OL,11,Fshe collided with Lukasova attempting
OL,12,Fto get her toe a ball that hung in the
OL,13,Fair. She picked up a yellow card for
OL,14,Fher challenge.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1781179881
OL,3,CWales secure top spot in World Cup
OL,4,Cqualifying after win over Czech
OL,5,CRepublic
OL,7,FChances were at a premium but Cain's
OL,8,Fpace looked like it could cause
OL,9,Fproblems. And so it transpired towards
OL,10,Fthe end of the half as she raced in
OL,11,Fbehind and nipped the ball beyond
OL,12,FLukasova, who had rushed well outside
OL,13,Fher area to a ball she never looked
OL,14,Ffavourite to gather.
OL,16,FBut when Cain fired it into the box
OL,17,Ffrom out wide, Carrie Jones, under
OL,18,Fpressure, couldn't direct it into an
OL,19,Fempty net.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1781179881
OL,3,CWales secure top spot in World Cup
OL,4,Cqualifying after win over Czech
OL,5,CRepublic
OL,7,FWales hit the front early in the
OL,8,Fsecond half. Ceri Holland's clipped
OL,9,Ffree-kick found Gemma Evans completely
OL,10,Funmarked in the middle of the Czech
OL,11,Fbox. Lukasova got nowhere near it and
OL,12,FEvans glanced her head into an empty
OL,13,Fnet.
OL,15,FAs the half wore on, Wales' energy
OL,16,Flevels dipped and the visitors
OL,17,Fappeared to lack the quality to take
OL,18,Fadvantage. A stalemate developed with
OL,19,FCzech Republic controlling the ball
OL,20,Fbut unable to do anything with it.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1781179881
OL,3,CWales secure top spot in World Cup
OL,4,Cqualifying after win over Czech
OL,5,CRepublic
OL,7,FBut with 15 minutes to go, Holland
OL,8,Ffound that burst of energy he side
OL,9,Fneeded. She ran from inside her own
OL,10,Fhalf, beyond the visiting defence, and
OL,11,Fsquared it to Mared Griffiths, who had
OL,12,Fthe easiest of tap-ins to make it 3-1.
OL,14,FIt was a goal that took the sting out
OL,15,Fof the game. The visitors rattled the
OL,16,Fcross bar in injury time but Wales
OL,17,Fwere able to see out the rest of the
OL,18,Fcontest without too many stressful
OL,19,Fmoments.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
