PN,46608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1781179881
OL,3,CWales secure top spot in World Cup
OL,4,Cqualifying after win over Czech
OL,5,CRepublic
OL,7,FWales will now head into the play-off
OL,8,Fphase of qualification for the World
OL,9,FCup. They will have to win at least
OL,10,Ftwo play-off ties, both two legs each,
OL,11,Fto reach the tournament.
OL,13,FThey will discover their opponents
OL,14,Fwhen the draw is made on June 24.
OL,16,FWales: Middleton-Patel; Roberts,
OL,17,FDavies, Evans, Woodham; James (C),
OL,18,FIngle, Jones; Holland, Cain, Griffiths.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
